OL,3,CWorker stole #15k from church to pay
OL,4,Cfor Sky TV and fund 'shopping
OL,5,Caddiction'
OL,7,FA former church administrator with an
OL,8,F"addiction to shopping" stole #15,000
OL,9,Ffrom her employer - using church funds
OL,10,Fto pay for her Sky TV, petrol and
OL,11,FAmazon goods.
OL,13,FClaire Clarke worked for St Mary
OL,14,FMagdalen Church in Torquay from home
OL,15,Fduring the pandemic.
OL,17,FShe has now admitted stealing #15,000
OL,18,Ffrom the church.
