OL,3,CWorker stole #15k from church to pay
OL,4,Cfor Sky TV and fund 'shopping
OL,5,Caddiction'
OL,7,FThe 44-year-old from Paignton first
OL,8,Flinked the church's credit card to her
OL,9,FSky TV account. She then started using
OL,10,Fthe card to pay for other items - from
OL,11,Fsmall amounts of food to petrol and
OL,12,Fgoods on her Amazon account.
OL,14,FShe was eventually found out and
OL,15,Flocked out of the church accounts, but
OL,16,Fnot before her spending spree had used
OL,17,F#14,899 of church funds.
OL,19,FThe court heard she was ill at the
OL,20,Ftime and had "an addiction to
OL,21,Fshopping".
