OL,3,CWorker stole #15k from church to pay
OL,4,Cfor Sky TV and fund 'shopping
OL,5,Caddiction'
OL,7,FClarke admitted one charge of theft
OL,8,Ffrom her employer. She wept as she was
OL,9,Fsentenced at a hearing at Exeter Crown
OL,10,FCourt on Tuesday 15 October.
OL,12,FIn a statement Reverend Samuel Leach
OL,13,Fsaid he was "mortified" when he found
OL,14,Fout what had been going on.
OL,16,F"I felt betrayed, sick to my stomach
OL,17,Fthat someone in such a position could
OL,18,Fdo this," he said.
