OL,7,FThe judge, Recorder Zoey Saunders,
OL,8,Facknowledged Clarke had no previous
OL,9,Fconvictions, her full admissions of
OL,10,Fguilt and genuine remorse and the
OL,11,Fspirit of forgiveness in the community.
OL,13,FShe was sentenced to two years in
OL,14,Fprison suspended for 18 months.
OL,16,FInsurers have paid #10,000 towards the
OL,17,Flosses.
